title: Death of an Internet star
author: VD
content_html: Sunny Lucas died on Tuesday, July 21st. The void she leaves behind in the electronic firmament will be much regretted by canine-lovers around the world. Our condolences to Rachel and the rest of the Lucas family.
content_text:
Sunny Lucas died
on Tuesday, July 21st.  The void she leaves behind in the electronic firmament will be much regretted by canine-lovers around the world.  Our condolences to Rachel and the rest of the Lucas family.
